{"tid":1403314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣唔好係炮仗到炒車!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:10:41.000Z","uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55aada489da6b725455a812fccca2732617b765b","tid":1403314,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"文宣唔好係炮仗到炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先有幾條片都影唔到有火光係天上掉野...<br />\n只係見到地面爆開...<br />\n<br />\n仲有一條片就係示威者傘陣入面有火光...<br />\n明顯係點火之後先爆炸...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講,你要炮仗係點完火之後,係高空掉落黎.<br />\n仲要計好時間係地面爆開...<br />\n毅進仔係無咁好計算能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩唔好炒車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0ae50311f9ffb18813075b905e8d3999f13363","tid":1403314,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972d1d8e0f361b59312d170f4e6adc00818b0678","tid":1403314,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:35:57.000Z","msg":"現場地下點火一早俾人發現啦"},{"pid":"8d6277eb0e3b90a0d28a71e37e82c229e91c2ff8","tid":1403314,"uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"972d1d8e0f361b59312d1